trans-unit.source: Because you are using Firefox, you will need to manually restart your browser after installation.
trans-unit.target: Because you are using Firefox, you will need to manually restart your browser after installation.

trans-unit.source: Why do I have to restart Firefox?
trans-unit.target: Why do I have to restart Firefox?

trans-unit.source: We use trusted certificates to secure the communication between browser and card reader. During the installation, these certificates are added to the keychain, a collection of trusted certificates on your computer.
trans-unit.target: We use trusted certificates to secure the communication between browser and card reader. During the installation, these certificates are added to the keychain, a collection of trusted certificates on your computer.

trans-unit.source: Most browsers use the operating system keychain, but Firefox has opted to use its own, separate, keychain. Because Firefox only reads the contents of this keychain when it is (re)started, we unfortunately have no other option but to do a full restart after the installation.
trans-unit.target: Most browsers use the operating system keychain, but Firefox has opted to use its own, separate, keychain. Because Firefox only reads the contents of this keychain when it is (re)started, we unfortunately have no other option but to do a full restart after the installation.
